Detailed Description

The RDF representation for type="http://www.cellml.org/RDF/API"

Member Data Documentation

attribute DataSource rdf_api::RDFAPIRepresentation::source

The RDF DataSource being represented. This is created afresh from the contents of the model every time you fetch it, and if you assign to it, then the RDF/XML in the model will be updated from it. However, changes made to the DataSource will not appear in the model until such an assignment is made.
